1
00:00:18,580 --> 00:00:21,420
♪Wearing peach blossom makeup,
I boil tea over the stove♪

2
00:00:23,060 --> 00:00:25,780
♪With a pure heart,
I embroider the brocade of time♪

3
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:31,380
♪On the short paper,
affection flows in the silent moonlight♪

4
00:00:31,820 --> 00:00:34,940
♪I only wish that by my side,
is my love♪

5
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:39,940
♪Cool autumn wind blowing,
I gaze far leaning against the railing♪

6
00:00:41,620 --> 00:00:44,460
♪Sunset glow over the green hill,
in formation wild geese are flying♪

7
00:00:45,940 --> 00:00:50,020
♪Covering a thousand miles on horseback,
for whom is he longing♪

8
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:53,620
♪He returned home in dreams♪

9
00:00:54,060 --> 00:00:58,220
♪I will never forget
that you held my hands♪

10
00:00:58,740 --> 00:01:03,020
♪In your warm palms
and we braved winds and waves♪

11
00:01:03,380 --> 00:01:08,300
♪Unexpectedly, after we traveled so far
and turned grey-haired♪

12
00:01:08,580 --> 00:01:11,660
♪I am still by your side♪

13
00:01:12,580 --> 00:01:16,740
♪Hearts burning,
we look into each other's eyes♪

14
00:01:17,180 --> 00:01:21,260
♪Feelings overflowing,
they don't need to be hided♪

15
00:01:21,820 --> 00:01:26,500
♪No matter how time passes
and life changes♪

16
00:01:27,100 --> 00:01:30,860
♪Together, we will grow old♪

17
00:01:32,420 --> 00:01:36,380
=The Sword and the Brocade=

18
00:01:36,900 --> 00:01:39,580
=Episode 4=

19
00:01:40,140 --> 00:01:41,020
Why did Wang Family suddenly

20
00:01:41,180 --> 00:01:42,540
change their mind?

21
00:01:43,060 --> 00:01:43,900
Didn't they say

22
00:01:44,020 --> 00:01:45,540
they wanted Erniang

23
00:01:45,700 --> 00:01:47,300
to marry into their family?

24
00:01:49,700 --> 00:01:50,700
Who knows?

25
00:01:51,580 --> 00:01:52,460
Madam Jiang

26
00:01:52,660 --> 00:01:54,340
visited us all of a sudden yesterday

27
00:01:54,460 --> 00:01:56,140
and said they wanted Shiyi instead.

28
00:01:56,380 --> 00:01:57,860
I told them I'd think about it.

29
00:01:57,980 --> 00:01:59,060
But they seemed to be very determined

30
00:01:59,180 --> 00:02:00,460
about marrying Shiyi,

31
00:02:00,580 --> 00:02:01,780
saying they'd agree to any terms

32
00:02:01,860 --> 00:02:02,900
as long as Shiyi

33
00:02:03,020 --> 00:02:05,180
is willing to marry.

34
00:02:06,100 --> 00:02:07,940
No matter who marries into Wang Family,

35
00:02:08,140 --> 00:02:10,460
it'd be a great effort made
for Zhun's marriage.

36
00:02:11,820 --> 00:02:12,700
It's just that Shiyi

37
00:02:12,820 --> 00:02:14,900
has been involved that day.

38
00:02:15,460 --> 00:02:16,620
I'm afraid...

39
00:02:16,740 --> 00:02:18,820
I think it's actually better.

40
00:02:19,700 --> 00:02:21,700
Shiyi is an independent-minded woman,

41
00:02:21,820 --> 00:02:22,900
who is hard to control.

42
00:02:23,700 --> 00:02:25,420
We may as well just marry Shiyi

43
00:02:25,500 --> 00:02:26,900
off to Wang Family as they want.

44
00:02:28,420 --> 00:02:29,860
As for what happened that day,

45
00:02:30,500 --> 00:02:32,780
as long as Concubine Lv is in my hands,

46
00:02:33,100 --> 00:02:35,420
I'm sure she'll keep quiet.

47
00:02:36,820 --> 00:02:37,700
Fine.

48
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:40,340
At the moment, Zhun's marriage

49
00:02:40,420 --> 00:02:41,740
matters the most.

50
00:02:43,580 --> 00:02:45,980
If we lose the support of the Jiangs,

51
00:02:46,700 --> 00:02:48,500
it'd be no use no matter

52
00:02:49,140 --> 00:02:50,700
which sister marries into our family.

53
00:02:51,900 --> 00:02:53,220
Erniang has been

54
00:02:53,620 --> 00:02:54,740
sending over some

55
00:02:54,820 --> 00:02:56,580
small gadgets lately.

56
00:02:57,260 --> 00:02:58,700
Zhun likes them a lot.

57
00:02:59,300 --> 00:03:01,180
I guess it's destiny.

58
00:03:03,300 --> 00:03:04,740
Then it's settled.

59
00:03:15,020 --> 00:03:15,900
My Lord!

60
00:03:17,260 --> 00:03:18,180
Qingtong.

61
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:20,700
My Lord!

62
00:03:21,220 --> 00:03:22,340
What are you doing?

63
00:03:22,460 --> 00:03:23,500
-Rise!
-My Lord!

64
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:24,820
My Lord!

65
00:03:26,340 --> 00:03:27,940
My Lord! I'm begging you!

66
00:03:28,940 --> 00:03:29,700
Please don't!

67
00:03:29,820 --> 00:03:30,860
Please don't marry Shiyi

68
00:03:30,980 --> 00:03:32,540
off to that Wang Yu!

69
00:03:33,220 --> 00:03:35,100
All the people in the capital

70
00:03:35,260 --> 00:03:36,940
know what kind person

71
00:03:36,940 --> 00:03:38,620
he is, My Lord!

72
00:03:39,300 --> 00:03:40,940
If Shiyi marries him,

73
00:03:41,540 --> 00:03:43,620
she'll live in utter misery!

74
00:03:43,620 --> 00:03:44,540
My Lord!

75
00:03:45,260 --> 00:03:46,540
I don't want her

76
00:03:46,660 --> 00:03:47,900
to marry Wang Yu either.

77
00:03:48,020 --> 00:03:49,700
But this marriage matters

78
00:03:49,820 --> 00:03:51,700
to the fortune of our entire Luo Family

79
00:03:51,820 --> 00:03:53,100
and Marquis Yongping's Mansion,

80
00:03:53,220 --> 00:03:55,780
we can't just cancel it.

81
00:03:56,180 --> 00:03:56,980
My Lord,

82
00:03:58,140 --> 00:03:59,300
I've gone through

83
00:04:00,060 --> 00:04:01,700
all the hardships

84
00:04:02,260 --> 00:04:03,340
in Yuhang

85
00:04:04,140 --> 00:04:05,540
for the last three years.

86
00:04:06,540 --> 00:04:07,700
But, My Lord,

87
00:04:07,860 --> 00:04:08,980
Shiyi is

88
00:04:09,100 --> 00:04:11,020
your daughter for God's sake!

89
00:04:11,140 --> 00:04:12,740
Will you just sit back and watch

90
00:04:12,860 --> 00:04:14,620
her life being destroyed?

91
00:04:14,740 --> 00:04:17,460
My Lord! Please!

92
00:04:17,860 --> 00:04:18,380
For

93
00:04:18,500 --> 00:04:20,180
old times' sake,

94
00:04:20,380 --> 00:04:23,180
please help Shiyi, My Lord!

95
00:04:23,180 --> 00:04:25,260
My Lord, I'm begging you!

96
00:04:25,620 --> 00:04:26,580
My Lord!

97
00:04:27,300 --> 00:04:29,340
My Lord, I'm begging you!

98
00:04:30,420 --> 00:04:30,980
I'm begging you!

99
00:04:30,980 --> 00:04:32,060
I'll go discuss it

100
00:04:32,220 --> 00:04:33,780
with my wife.

101
00:04:35,180 --> 00:04:36,180
Rise! Please rise!

102
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:37,580
Come on! Rise!

103
00:05:08,180 --> 00:05:09,620
My Lord, you are back.

104
00:05:13,260 --> 00:05:13,980
My Lady.

105
00:05:14,820 --> 00:05:15,620
Sit down.

106
00:05:25,260 --> 00:05:26,180
My Lady,

107
00:05:27,220 --> 00:05:28,340
I think

108
00:05:29,180 --> 00:05:31,940
we should cancel
the marriage arrangement

109
00:05:32,780 --> 00:05:34,500
with Duke Mao's Mansion.

110
00:05:43,820 --> 00:05:44,620
My Lord,

111
00:05:45,620 --> 00:05:47,100
the future of Zhun

112
00:05:47,380 --> 00:05:48,860
and Luo Family

113
00:05:49,380 --> 00:05:50,580
all depends

114
00:05:50,660 --> 00:05:51,780
on this marriage.

115
00:05:52,500 --> 00:05:54,780
How can we cancel it?

116
00:05:55,700 --> 00:05:56,780
But that Wang Yu

117
00:05:56,900 --> 00:05:58,900
is an infamous playboy.

118
00:05:59,380 --> 00:06:01,660
He... he's not only a frequenter

119
00:06:01,740 --> 00:06:02,660
of those entertainment venues,

120
00:06:02,740 --> 00:06:03,940
but also a ruthless

121
00:06:04,020 --> 00:06:05,100
and cruel bully!

122
00:06:05,220 --> 00:06:06,820
How can you push my daughter

123
00:06:06,940 --> 00:06:08,500
into an abyss of pain?

124
00:06:10,140 --> 00:06:11,100
Abyss of pain?

125
00:06:11,860 --> 00:06:13,380
All my dowries have been used

126
00:06:13,460 --> 00:06:15,380
to help out our family these years!

127
00:06:15,780 --> 00:06:18,100
I can't believe
you still don't trust me!

128
00:06:23,100 --> 00:06:24,340
I didn't

129
00:06:24,660 --> 00:06:26,740
mean that.

130
00:06:27,420 --> 00:06:28,700
I just...

131
00:06:39,180 --> 00:06:40,100
My Lord,

132
00:06:41,340 --> 00:06:42,500
as a concubine's daughter,

133
00:06:42,820 --> 00:06:44,940
it's a bliss for her that she can

134
00:06:45,220 --> 00:06:47,460
marry into Wang Family and become

135
00:06:47,940 --> 00:06:49,500
the wife of Duke Mao!

136
00:06:49,700 --> 00:06:51,580
It's a great bliss!

137
00:06:52,740 --> 00:06:55,380
It makes sense,

138
00:06:55,700 --> 00:06:57,140
and I know

139
00:06:57,300 --> 00:06:58,660
you are thinking of Zhun

140
00:06:58,740 --> 00:07:00,300
and our Luo Family.

141
00:07:00,620 --> 00:07:02,940
But my daughter isn't willing to marry.

142
00:07:03,820 --> 00:07:05,380
As her father,

143
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:07,980
how can I force her to do it?

144
00:07:13,380 --> 00:07:14,660
Marriage should

145
00:07:14,780 --> 00:07:16,180
be arranged by parents

146
00:07:16,300 --> 00:07:17,580
and matchmakers.

147
00:07:18,180 --> 00:07:20,100
It's not up to the children.

148
00:07:22,580 --> 00:07:23,900
My Lord, no worries!

149
00:07:24,140 --> 00:07:25,340
I will

150
00:07:25,500 --> 00:07:28,180
convince her to get on
that sedan willingly.

151
00:07:42,620 --> 00:07:43,580
Fine.

152
00:07:54,700 --> 00:07:55,740
Shiyi,

153
00:07:56,300 --> 00:07:57,940
don't worry too much.

154
00:07:58,060 --> 00:07:59,460
I've begged your father.

155
00:07:59,860 --> 00:08:02,180
After all you are his daughter,

156
00:08:02,300 --> 00:08:03,180
he won't let you

157
00:08:03,340 --> 00:08:05,020
marry that Wang Yu.

158
00:08:05,340 --> 00:08:06,020
Mom,

159
00:08:07,780 --> 00:08:08,740
don't you remember

160
00:08:08,900 --> 00:08:10,300
that we were sent to Yuhang

161
00:08:10,420 --> 00:08:11,780
right after you had a miscarriage.

162
00:08:12,940 --> 00:08:14,860
Although my father cared about us,

163
00:08:14,980 --> 00:08:15,700
he still had to listen

164
00:08:15,820 --> 00:08:16,740
to his wife.

165
00:08:17,460 --> 00:08:19,820
Now that this marriage matters
to the interests of our family,

166
00:08:19,980 --> 00:08:21,860
it won't be a big deal

167
00:08:21,980 --> 00:08:22,820
for him

168
00:08:22,940 --> 00:08:24,060
to sacrifice his concubine's daughter.

169
00:08:27,740 --> 00:08:30,020
And I heard that ever since His Lordship

170
00:08:30,180 --> 00:08:31,740
came back home for mourning,

171
00:08:31,900 --> 00:08:33,020
our family has been using

172
00:08:33,100 --> 00:08:34,820
his wife's dowries for expenses.

173
00:08:35,380 --> 00:08:37,020
I'm afraid that His Lordship

174
00:08:37,540 --> 00:08:38,460
can't call the shots now.

175
00:08:45,260 --> 00:08:46,820
Take both of them down!

176
00:08:48,700 --> 00:08:49,300
What?

177
00:08:51,300 --> 00:08:52,580
What? What's...

178
00:08:53,260 --> 00:08:54,220
Your Ladyship!

179
00:08:54,340 --> 00:08:55,500
Your Ladyship! What's going on?

180
00:08:55,500 --> 00:08:56,060
Mother,

181
00:08:56,060 --> 00:08:57,220
have we done anything wrong?

182
00:08:59,540 --> 00:09:02,100
You should recognize this, right?

183
00:09:04,020 --> 00:09:04,900
My Lady!

184
00:09:05,100 --> 00:09:06,060
Shiyi,

185
00:09:06,540 --> 00:09:08,340
how dare you

186
00:09:08,820 --> 00:09:10,420
secretly sell the embroideries?

187
00:09:10,700 --> 00:09:12,180
Hasn't our Luo Family

188
00:09:12,340 --> 00:09:13,660
provided you enough food and clothes?

189
00:09:13,820 --> 00:09:14,900
Your Ladyship,

190
00:09:15,100 --> 00:09:16,620
we'd never dare do that!

191
00:09:16,740 --> 00:09:17,140
It...

192
00:09:17,180 --> 00:09:18,780
it's probably a misunderstanding!

193
00:09:18,940 --> 00:09:19,660
Misunderstanding?

194
00:09:20,500 --> 00:09:22,060
The embroideries were retrieved

195
00:09:22,060 --> 00:09:23,020
from Xianling Pavilion.

196
00:09:23,180 --> 00:09:24,340
It can't be a mistake!

197
00:09:25,140 --> 00:09:26,820
Mother, I think it's a misunderstanding.

198
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:27,900
Master Jian of Xianling Pavilion

199
00:09:28,020 --> 00:09:29,340
is my teacher.

200
00:09:29,460 --> 00:09:30,860
I just wanted to show
her the embroideries

201
00:09:31,020 --> 00:09:32,500
to get her instructions.

202
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:33,620
Fine.

203
00:09:33,820 --> 00:09:34,900
I'll call Master Jian over

204
00:09:35,060 --> 00:09:36,260
and ask her!

205
00:09:36,460 --> 00:09:37,460
Your Ladyship!

206
00:09:38,100 --> 00:09:38,860
Your Ladyship!

207
00:09:39,060 --> 00:09:40,580
I should be held accountable for this!

208
00:09:40,700 --> 00:09:42,060
It's my fault!

209
00:09:42,180 --> 00:09:43,140
It's me...

210
00:09:43,300 --> 00:09:43,940
It's me who saw

211
00:09:44,100 --> 00:09:45,580
Shiyi's exquisite works

212
00:09:45,740 --> 00:09:46,940
and asked her to sell them for money!

213
00:09:47,060 --> 00:09:48,180
I was being greedy.

214
00:09:48,260 --> 00:09:49,700
Please punish me!

215
00:09:49,700 --> 00:09:50,500
No! It's not true!

216
00:09:50,580 --> 00:09:51,660
It's all my fault!

217
00:09:51,780 --> 00:09:52,500
I'm the one who stole

218
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:53,300
Lady Shiyi's embroideries

219
00:09:53,380 --> 00:09:54,060
and sold them for money!

220
00:09:54,180 --> 00:09:55,940
Your Ladyship, you should punish me!

221
00:09:56,100 --> 00:09:57,900
What nonsense are you talking about?

222
00:09:58,020 --> 00:09:59,740
Since you've all admitted it,

223
00:09:59,980 --> 00:10:00,820
Fine!

224
00:10:01,180 --> 00:10:01,940
Guards,

225
00:10:02,460 --> 00:10:05,180
flog each of them 20 times!

226
00:10:05,780 --> 00:10:06,540
Mother!

227
00:10:13,940 --> 00:10:14,940
Nanny Xu.

228
00:10:15,060 --> 00:10:15,580
Yes!

229
00:10:15,700 --> 00:10:16,900
Count carefully!

230
00:10:16,980 --> 00:10:17,620
Yes!

231
00:10:18,260 --> 00:10:19,300
One!

232
00:10:20,340 --> 00:10:21,260
Mom!

233
00:10:26,380 --> 00:10:28,500
Mother, it's my bad!

234
00:10:28,660 --> 00:10:29,580
I'm the one who sold the embroideries!

235
00:10:29,660 --> 00:10:31,020
They have nothing to do with it!

236
00:10:31,180 --> 00:10:32,060
Two!

237
00:10:34,380 --> 00:10:35,300
Shiyi,

238
00:10:35,740 --> 00:10:37,180
you didn't do anything wrong.

239
00:10:38,100 --> 00:10:39,700
How can I punish you?

240
00:10:39,820 --> 00:10:40,860
I was wrong!

241
00:10:40,980 --> 00:10:42,220
It's really my fault!

242
00:10:42,340 --> 00:10:44,020
Please punish me instead!

243
00:10:44,180 --> 00:10:44,940
Three!

244
00:10:50,740 --> 00:10:51,700
Shiyi,

245
00:10:52,420 --> 00:10:53,660
as your mother, I have

246
00:10:55,020 --> 00:10:57,020
to teach you a lesson today.

247
00:10:57,540 --> 00:11:00,460
Nothing can be done without rules.

248
00:11:00,860 --> 00:11:01,740
Four!

249
00:11:03,420 --> 00:11:04,380
In our Luo Family,

250
00:11:05,380 --> 00:11:07,260
I'm the one who sets the rules!

251
00:11:07,820 --> 00:11:08,700
Five!

252
00:11:17,900 --> 00:11:18,740
Six!

253
00:11:20,940 --> 00:11:21,580
Mother!

254
00:11:25,580 --> 00:11:27,300
I know I made a mistake!

255
00:11:28,300 --> 00:11:29,540
From now on,

256
00:11:30,140 --> 00:11:32,340
I will behave myself

257
00:11:32,660 --> 00:11:34,340
and I'll never break the rules again!

258
00:11:51,020 --> 00:11:51,860
Shiyi,

259
00:11:53,380 --> 00:11:55,500
I know you are a sensible person.

260
00:11:56,260 --> 00:11:58,380
Then I'll let it go today.

261
00:11:58,900 --> 00:12:00,180
If it happens again,

262
00:12:00,620 --> 00:12:02,140
I won't let you off so easily!

263
00:12:11,620 --> 00:12:16,180
(Duke Mao's Mansion)

264
00:12:24,460 --> 00:12:25,460
Sir.

265
00:12:27,980 --> 00:12:28,700
It's burning hot!

266
00:12:31,220 --> 00:12:32,620
You are so clumsy!

267
00:12:32,700 --> 00:12:33,900
Get out of here!

268
00:12:34,060 --> 00:12:34,660
Yes.

269
00:12:42,380 --> 00:12:44,500
Mother, Luo Family has really agreed!

270
00:12:44,620 --> 00:12:45,660
Of course!

271
00:12:46,140 --> 00:12:48,300
Have I ever lied to you?

272
00:12:48,860 --> 00:12:49,820
It's great!

273
00:12:49,980 --> 00:12:51,300
You didn't let me down indeed!

274
00:12:51,460 --> 00:12:52,380
You love me so much!

275
00:12:53,060 --> 00:12:54,500
But I don't understand

276
00:12:54,660 --> 00:12:56,060
why do you insist

277
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:57,620
on marrying Luo Shiyi?

278
00:12:58,180 --> 00:12:59,620
Based on your sister,

279
00:12:59,780 --> 00:13:01,740
Erniang is witty and smart;

280
00:13:01,940 --> 00:13:03,460
she's the most outstanding one

281
00:13:03,580 --> 00:13:04,820
among all her sisters.

282
00:13:05,060 --> 00:13:06,140
What would my sister know?

283
00:13:07,420 --> 00:13:08,020
Alright.

284
00:13:10,060 --> 00:13:10,980
Why are you leaving?

285
00:13:11,140 --> 00:13:11,900
You won't eat anymore?

286
00:13:11,900 --> 00:13:13,340
I'll marry a beauty soon! I'm full!

287
00:13:15,020 --> 00:13:16,460
Ridiculous! This kid!

288
00:13:33,260 --> 00:13:33,980
Mom,

289
00:13:34,620 --> 00:13:36,140
you are seriously injured.

290
00:13:36,300 --> 00:13:38,020
Do not move!

291
