I was just flogged six times.

292
00:13:41,740 --> 00:13:42,980
I'll be better

293
00:13:43,180 --> 00:13:44,580
after applying medicine.

294
00:13:46,220 --> 00:13:48,540
By the way, how's Dongqing?

295
00:13:50,140 --> 00:13:51,500
I've applied medicine for her

296
00:13:51,620 --> 00:13:52,540
and let her rest.

297
00:13:54,780 --> 00:13:56,340
Dongqing is such

298
00:13:56,980 --> 00:13:58,420
a loyal maid.

299
00:13:59,660 --> 00:14:02,300
You've been treating her
like your younger sister.

300
00:14:02,300 --> 00:14:03,860
It's really paid off.

301
00:14:04,380 --> 00:14:06,980
Mother, it's my bad!

302
00:14:07,340 --> 00:14:08,860
I wasn't cautious enough

303
00:14:08,940 --> 00:14:10,700
and let Her Ladyship find out.

304
00:14:10,820 --> 00:14:12,020
Sorry I made you suffer!

305
00:14:12,660 --> 00:14:13,580
My daughter,

306
00:14:14,180 --> 00:14:15,540
don't be silly.

307
00:14:16,500 --> 00:14:17,740
I'm the one

308
00:14:18,260 --> 00:14:20,100
who brought trouble to you.

309
00:14:20,660 --> 00:14:21,900
Her Ladyship

310
00:14:21,980 --> 00:14:23,180
knows that I'm

311
00:14:23,460 --> 00:14:25,220
your weakness,

312
00:14:25,700 --> 00:14:27,620
that's why she used me against you.

313
00:14:29,100 --> 00:14:31,820
I feel sorry that I'm so useless

314
00:14:32,140 --> 00:14:33,860
that I can't be of any help.

315
00:14:34,940 --> 00:14:36,180
But, Shiyi,

316
00:14:36,540 --> 00:14:37,900
I've thought about it.

317
00:14:38,420 --> 00:14:40,260
I can't let you marry off

318
00:14:40,620 --> 00:14:42,780
to Wang Family whatsoever!

319
00:14:43,740 --> 00:14:45,180
Tomorrow morning,

320
00:14:45,540 --> 00:14:47,500
I'll go to Duke Mao's Mansion

321
00:14:47,620 --> 00:14:48,740
and talk to Madam Wang.

322
00:14:48,860 --> 00:14:50,460
I'll tell her

323
00:14:50,660 --> 00:14:52,620
that you've been suffering from a

324
00:14:52,740 --> 00:14:54,100
coughing problem since you were little.

325
00:14:55,100 --> 00:14:57,620
Maybe it'll make her change her mind.

326
00:14:59,500 --> 00:15:01,020
But I'm also worried

327
00:15:01,460 --> 00:15:02,780
that it'd make it difficult

328
00:15:03,180 --> 00:15:04,780
for you to get married

329
00:15:04,900 --> 00:15:05,780
in the future.

330
00:15:05,900 --> 00:15:06,700
Mom,

331
00:15:07,900 --> 00:15:09,780
you always put me first.

332
00:15:09,900 --> 00:15:11,420
What about yourself?

333
00:15:11,660 --> 00:15:13,500
If you ruin Her Ladyship's plan,

334
00:15:13,580 --> 00:15:15,300
she'll never forgive you!

335
00:15:15,460 --> 00:15:16,500
Kid,

336
00:15:17,460 --> 00:15:19,220
as long as you are well and happy,

337
00:15:20,060 --> 00:15:22,060
I'd love to do anything.

338
00:15:30,940 --> 00:15:31,740
It's okay.

339
00:15:31,980 --> 00:15:33,300
Don't worry.

340
00:15:33,780 --> 00:15:35,220
I'll figure out something.

341
00:15:36,500 --> 00:15:37,060
Stop worrying.

342
00:15:48,220 --> 00:15:49,140
It'll be fine.

343
00:15:51,020 --> 00:15:51,700
Mom,

344
00:15:53,780 --> 00:15:55,100
let's leave here!

345
00:15:56,420 --> 00:15:58,100
Let's leave on the 1st of next month!

346
00:15:58,220 --> 00:15:59,580
We'll never come back again!

347
00:16:00,500 --> 00:16:01,020
Well...

348
00:16:01,500 --> 00:16:02,380
Mother, don't move!

349
00:16:02,460 --> 00:16:03,500
What are you talking about?

350
00:16:05,220 --> 00:16:06,820
You want to run away from your wedding?

351
00:16:07,620 --> 00:16:08,820
Listen, kid!

352
00:16:08,900 --> 00:16:10,060
You can't do that!

353
00:16:10,460 --> 00:16:10,940
But...

354
00:16:11,020 --> 00:16:11,620
how come you've never

355
