356
00:16:13,540 --> 00:16:14,980
I was worried that you'd object,

357
00:16:15,140 --> 00:16:16,620
so I dared not tell you.

358
00:16:17,460 --> 00:16:19,020
No! You can't do that, kid!

359
00:16:19,540 --> 00:16:20,420
If... If you were caught

360
00:16:20,460 --> 00:16:21,500
by Her Ladyship,

361
00:16:21,580 --> 00:16:23,580
she'd break your legs!

362
00:16:23,900 --> 00:16:24,500
No!

363
00:16:24,660 --> 00:16:26,100
It's too risky!

364
00:16:26,900 --> 00:16:27,900
Besides,

365
00:16:27,980 --> 00:16:30,540
Even... even if we can
run away successfully,

366
00:16:30,780 --> 00:16:31,380
how can we

367
00:16:31,460 --> 00:16:32,740
survive on our own?

368
00:16:32,980 --> 00:16:34,940
Mom, don't worry about it!

369
00:16:35,020 --> 00:16:36,500
We can live

370
00:16:36,500 --> 00:16:37,500
on my embroideries!

371
00:16:37,740 --> 00:16:39,060
With my skills,

372
00:16:39,140 --> 00:16:40,180
we can totally

373
00:16:40,300 --> 00:16:41,060
make a living at them!

374
00:16:41,460 --> 00:16:42,620
You don't need to worry!

375
00:16:45,260 --> 00:16:46,620
I don't think it'll work.

376
00:16:47,420 --> 00:16:49,380
With our current situation,

377
00:16:49,900 --> 00:16:53,540
I'm afraid even returning to Yuhang
would be hard for us.

378
00:16:53,780 --> 00:16:55,700
Mother, do you remember

379
00:16:55,780 --> 00:16:57,500
Mr. Lin who once saved us?

380
00:16:57,860 --> 00:16:58,580
We can take his boat

381
00:16:58,700 --> 00:16:59,860
and go back!

382
00:16:59,940 --> 00:17:01,060
We've made a plan.

383
00:17:01,140 --> 00:17:02,260
You don't have to worry.

384
00:17:15,020 --> 00:17:16,180
Shiyi,

385
00:17:17,340 --> 00:17:18,740
I didn't expect

386
00:17:19,420 --> 00:17:21,100
that you've arranged everything

387
00:17:21,100 --> 00:17:22,060
ahead of time!

388
00:17:23,620 --> 00:17:24,500
Looks like

389
00:17:24,580 --> 00:17:26,460
my daughter is a smart and brave

390
00:17:27,100 --> 00:17:29,220
grown-up now!

391
00:17:31,940 --> 00:17:32,700
Okay,

392
00:17:34,180 --> 00:17:35,500
I'll listen to you.

393
00:17:36,500 --> 00:17:39,220
I'd love to do anything

394
00:17:39,500 --> 00:17:41,180
as long as you are happy.

395
00:17:42,220 --> 00:17:44,020
No matter what will happen,

396
00:17:45,340 --> 00:17:47,020
I'll always have your back!

397
00:18:42,060 --> 00:18:43,540
One year ago,

398
00:18:45,340 --> 00:18:47,740
I personally made this wedding dress,

399
00:18:49,660 --> 00:18:51,020
hoping I can

400
00:18:51,660 --> 00:18:52,980
marry His Lordship

