414
00:20:08,340 --> 00:20:09,220
But it's

415
00:20:09,340 --> 00:20:11,140
my own choice.

416
00:20:11,940 --> 00:20:12,780
And I won't

417
00:20:13,500 --> 00:20:15,380
regret it in the future.

418
00:20:19,580 --> 00:20:20,700
Good girl!

419
00:20:24,580 --> 00:20:26,260
Listen to me.

420
00:20:26,980 --> 00:20:28,740
Although you'll be a concubine,

421
00:20:29,660 --> 00:20:33,660
