440
00:21:29,220 --> 00:21:32,100
As long as you can win the Marquis over,

441
00:21:32,900 --> 00:21:35,020
and with the favor

442
00:21:35,100 --> 00:21:37,140
of the Great Madam,

443
00:21:37,300 --> 00:21:38,380
one day,

444
00:21:39,220 --> 00:21:41,380
if you give birth to His Lordship's child,

445
00:21:42,620 --> 00:21:43,780
no worries,

446
00:21:44,060 --> 00:21:46,660
with our Qiao Family having your back,

447
00:21:47,340 --> 00:21:51,300
everything's possible!

448
00:21:55,060 --> 00:21:59,260
I'll keep your words in mind, mother!

