00:22:31,620 --> 00:22:32,700
Concubine can't enter
from the front gate,

453
00:22:32,820 --> 00:22:33,820
but the side door only!

454
00:22:34,820 --> 00:22:35,220
You...

455
00:22:35,220 --> 00:22:35,820
Xiuyuan,

456
00:22:36,740 --> 00:22:37,780
we are new here.

457
00:22:37,900 --> 00:22:38,780
Don't make trouble.

458
00:22:40,180 --> 00:22:41,260
-Yes.
-Yes.

459
00:22:45,460 --> 00:22:46,220
Lift the sedan up!

460
00:23:15,460 --> 00:23:16,500
Young man.

461
00:23:17,220 --> 00:23:18,460
the sedan has to stop here.

462
00:23:18,860 --> 00:23:19,740
According to the rules,

463
00:23:19,820 --> 00:23:21,140
please let the bride walk in by herself.

464
00:23:22,100 --> 00:23:23,420
It's raining

465
00:23:23,540 --> 00:23:24,620
and the ground is all wet.

466
00:23:24,740 --> 00:23:26,180
