for the bride to walk in.

467
00:23:26,300 --> 00:23:28,420
Please make an exception for her

468
00:23:28,780 --> 00:23:30,940
and move the sedan to the yard.

469
00:23:33,740 --> 00:23:34,460
Okay.

470
00:23:35,660 --> 00:23:36,500
Lift the sedan up!

471
00:23:37,060 --> 00:23:38,300
Stop! Stop!

472
00:23:40,140 --> 00:23:41,780
Don't you know the rules?

473
00:23:45,500 --> 00:23:46,900
You are Nanny Zhang, right?

474
00:23:47,940 --> 00:23:49,020
Nanny Zhang,

475
00:23:49,180 --> 00:23:51,380
I'm Nanny Tao,
working for Her Ladyship.

476
00:23:52,340 --> 00:23:53,980
Nanny Zhang, you are not new,

477
00:23:54,100 --> 00:23:55,740
you should know better

478
00:23:55,820 --> 00:23:57,780
