479
00:23:58,780 --> 00:24:03,380
Please let Concubine Qiao get off the sedan
and walk in by herself.

480
00:24:03,860 --> 00:24:04,900
Nanny Tao,

481
00:24:05,060 --> 00:24:06,420
we know the rules,

482
00:24:06,500 --> 00:24:07,380
but it's...

483
00:24:07,460 --> 00:24:08,980
Rules should be obeyed.

484
00:24:10,140 --> 00:24:14,820
Please let Concubine Qiao get off the sedan
and walk in by herself,

