498
00:25:20,860 --> 00:25:21,380
Let's go!

499
00:25:31,060 --> 00:25:32,180
Put away the umbrella.

500
00:25:32,300 --> 00:25:33,420
My Lady!

501
00:25:36,220 --> 00:25:37,060
Put it away.

502
00:25:49,700 --> 00:25:50,940
Concubine Qiao,

503
00:25:51,060 --> 00:25:53,660
it's called 'flowing in wealth'!

504
00:26:48,700 --> 00:26:50,700
It's so late already!

505
00:26:51,300 --> 00:26:53,500
