506
00:26:54,060 --> 00:26:55,340
It's his wedding day

507
00:26:55,460 --> 00:26:56,900
with Lianfang!

508
00:26:57,140 --> 00:26:59,220
Mother, you worry too much.

509
00:26:59,340 --> 00:27:00,460
Everything will be fine.

510
00:27:01,260 --> 00:27:02,660
My fourth brother has been busy

511
00:27:02,780 --> 00:27:04,140
