512
00:27:04,460 --> 00:27:06,300
Perhaps he lost the track of time.

513
00:27:07,580 --> 00:27:09,740
Mother, His Lordship
carries big responsibilities.

514
00:27:09,860 --> 00:27:12,180
It's normal that he's too busy
to remember things.

515
00:27:12,700 --> 00:27:13,420
And now,

516
00:27:13,580 --> 00:27:14,260
Lingkuan and I

517
00:27:14,380 --> 00:27:15,620
