523
00:27:22,660 --> 00:27:23,660
Don't be so lazy!

524
00:27:25,380 --> 00:27:28,500
Dan Yang is as considerate as always.

525
00:27:30,180 --> 00:27:31,660
Yuanniang

526
00:27:32,020 --> 00:27:34,220
is capable and filial,

527
00:27:34,820 --> 00:27:36,860
but she's too strong-minded

528
00:27:37,460 --> 00:27:38,380
and always argues

529
00:27:38,500 --> 00:27:39,940
with Lingyi.

530
00:27:40,460 --> 00:27:41,660
I think

531
00:27:41,780 --> 00:27:43,980
Lianfang is understanding,

532
00:27:44,100 --> 00:27:46,460
and she really loves Lingyi.

533
00:27:46,580 --> 00:27:48,620
If she can become

534
00:27:48,780 --> 00:27:50,220
a good wife to Lingyi

535
00:27:50,340 --> 00:27:52,700
like you are to Kuan'er,

536
00:27:53,300 --> 00:27:55,820
I'll be so relieved.

537
00:27:56,220 --> 00:27:57,420
Mother, no worries.

538
00:27:57,540 --> 00:27:58,580
I'm sure His Lordship

539
00:27:58,700 --> 00:28:00,140
knows you care about him!

540
00:28:04,940 --> 00:28:06,260
Greetings, mother!

541
00:28:09,220 --> 00:28:10,580
Brother, sister-in-law.

542
00:28:10,780 --> 00:28:13,420
Yi'er, you are finally back!

543
00:28:13,540 --> 00:28:14,500
Go and

544
00:28:14,580 --> 00:28:16,580
