I'll serve you taking

579
00:30:42,500 --> 00:30:43,820
a bath now.

580
00:30:51,060 --> 00:30:52,300
I'm not a good person.

581
00:30:53,580 --> 00:30:54,780
Why do you try so hard?

582
00:30:56,180 --> 00:30:57,540
And how do you know

583
00:30:57,780 --> 00:30:59,500
that this is not something I want?

584
00:31:00,780 --> 00:31:02,740
Ever since I first met you,

585
00:31:04,220 --> 00:31:06,660
I've fallen in love with you.

586
00:31:19,700 --> 00:31:20,980
I can provide you

587
00:31:22,020 --> 00:31:23,540
with a peaceful, safe

588
00:31:25,100 --> 00:31:27,100
and wealthy life,

589
00:31:27,620 --> 00:31:28,020
but,

590
00:31:30,780 --> 00:31:32,020
nothing more than that.

591
00:31:33,100 --> 00:31:34,900
That's not what I want!

592
00:31:34,980 --> 00:31:37,180
I just want you to give me a chance!

593
00:31:44,260 --> 00:31:45,300
It's late.

594
00:31:46,820 --> 00:31:47,860
You should go to bed now.

595
00:31:49,700 --> 00:31:50,620
My Lord!

596
00:31:53,420 --> 00:31:55,060
My Lord, don't leave!

597
00:31:55,740 --> 00:31:56,900
Please stay here

598
00:31:57,700 --> 00:31:58,820
with me for one night!

599
00:31:59,780 --> 00:32:01,180
Just one night!

600
00:32:02,380 --> 00:32:03,380
Okay?

601
00:32:39,620 --> 00:32:41,060
It's just a beginning.

602
00:32:41,900 --> 00:32:44,340
I'm sure that I'll win your heart!

603
00:33:02,860 --> 00:33:04,140
My Lord, how come you are back?

604
00:33:11,860 --> 00:33:14,020
You and Concubine Qiao
just got married today.

605
00:33:18,700 --> 00:33:19,780
The other men would be so happy

606
00:33:19,860 --> 00:33:21,460
to have another wife.

607
00:33:21,580 --> 00:33:23,140
You are the only one

608
00:33:23,220 --> 00:33:24,580
who's bothered by this.

609
00:33:25,180 --> 00:33:27,180
You talk too much today!

610
00:33:29,980 --> 00:33:31,100
I am just worried

611
00:33:31,220 --> 00:33:31,980
about you.

612
00:33:32,500 --> 00:33:33,900
Both the court affairs and

613
00:33:33,980 --> 00:33:35,460
your marital life keep you occupied.

614
00:33:35,940 --> 00:33:36,620
Having a concubine

615
00:33:36,740 --> 00:33:38,060
is a sweet and lovely thing

616
00:33:38,140 --> 00:33:39,180
to the other men,

617
00:33:39,380 --> 00:33:40,860
yet to you,

618
00:33:41,060 --> 00:33:41,900
it's just

619
00:33:41,980 --> 00:33:43,340
more responsibility.

620
00:33:45,340 --> 00:33:47,860
Concubine Qiao married into
our Xu's all of a sudden.

621
00:33:48,100 --> 00:33:49,420
We should make her feel at home.

622
00:33:50,540 --> 00:33:51,980
Ask the servants to pay more attention

623
00:33:52,260 --> 00:33:53,740
and try their best to meet her needs.

624
00:33:53,940 --> 00:33:54,940
Take good care of her.

625
00:33:55,780 --> 00:33:57,060
Understood, My Lord.

626
00:34:02,780 --> 00:34:03,740
I'll take a rest now.

627
00:34:13,780 --> 00:34:14,940
It's said Concubine Qiao

628
00:34:15,020 --> 00:34:16,020
waited His Lordship till midnight,

629
00:34:16,140 --> 00:34:17,220
but His Lordship visited her

630
00:34:17,340 --> 00:34:18,220
only for a short period of time

631
00:34:18,260 --> 00:34:19,540
before heading back to
Half-moon Chamber,

632
00:34:19,580 --> 00:34:20,780
leaving Concubine Qiao sitting on the floor

633
00:34:20,900 --> 00:34:22,060
and crying for a long time!

634
00:34:22,540 --> 00:34:24,020
Really?

635
00:34:24,140 --> 00:34:25,780
I thought His Lordship

636
00:34:25,900 --> 00:34:27,820
would treat her differently
from the other two.

637
00:34:27,940 --> 00:34:29,620
Turns out this Qiao woman

638
00:34:29,740 --> 00:34:30,860
is just so-so!

639
00:34:31,140 --> 00:34:32,380
Tell me about it!

640
00:34:34,460 --> 00:34:35,620
Who are gossiping over there?

641
00:34:35,740 --> 00:34:36,860
Come out, now!

642
00:34:38,500 --> 00:34:39,500
-Great Madam!
-Great Madam!

643
00:34:39,660 --> 00:34:40,980
How dare you

644
00:34:41,060 --> 00:34:41,740
gossip about

645
00:34:41,860 --> 00:34:42,940
your Masters?

646
00:34:43,100 --> 00:34:44,340
Are you looking for death?

647
00:34:44,700 --> 00:34:46,420
Great Madam!
We made a mistake!

648
00:34:46,660 --> 00:34:47,540
Please spare our lives!

649
00:34:47,740 --> 00:34:49,180
We won't do it again!

650
00:34:58,980 --> 00:35:00,340
Get a human trafficker here.

651
00:35:00,860 --> 00:35:02,580
Let him sell these two!

652
00:35:03,620 --> 00:35:04,780
-Great Madam!
-Great Madam!

653
00:35:04,860 --> 00:35:05,900
-Great Madam!
-Great Madam!

654
00:35:05,980 --> 00:35:07,060
Great Madam! Please spare us!

655
00:35:07,140 --> 00:35:08,180
Great Madam!

656
00:35:12,220 --> 00:35:13,500
I came at a wrong time.

657
00:35:13,540 --> 00:35:15,580
Sorry I disturbed your breakfast,
Great Madam!

658
00:35:16,260 --> 00:35:18,060
Lianfang, you are here!

659
00:35:18,700 --> 00:35:20,460
I'm glad you came!

660
00:35:20,580 --> 00:35:21,820
I'm having breakfast alone.

661
00:35:21,820 --> 00:35:22,740
It's so boring.

662
00:35:22,900 --> 00:35:23,860
Have a seat.

663
00:35:24,300 --> 00:35:24,860
Here.

664
00:35:25,380 --> 00:35:26,580
Thank you, Great Madam!

665
00:35:29,740 --> 00:35:31,620
I know it's been hard for you.

666
00:35:31,700 --> 00:35:33,300
Look at your face.

667
00:35:33,340 --> 00:35:34,980
You are losing weight.

668
00:35:36,260 --> 00:35:37,860
His Lordship has been

669
00:35:37,900 --> 00:35:39,820
busy with the court affairs,

670
00:35:40,340 --> 00:35:42,980
so he's quite tired.

671
00:35:43,940 --> 00:35:46,180
Please try to understand him.

672
00:35:46,660 --> 00:35:47,980
Things will get better

673
00:35:48,100 --> 00:35:49,860
when he's free.

674
00:35:50,420 --> 00:35:52,060
His Lordship is busy every day.

675
00:35:52,300 --> 00:35:54,260
The best I can do for him

676
00:35:54,380 --> 00:35:56,100
is taking good care of myself.

677
00:35:57,140 --> 00:35:59,180
Good! Good!

678
00:36:00,860 --> 00:36:01,940
Great Madam,

679
00:36:02,580 --> 00:36:03,620
in a few days,

680
00:36:03,700 --> 00:36:04,780
you'll go to Ci'an Temple

681
00:36:04,860 --> 00:36:06,060
and pray for our family.

682
00:36:06,180 --> 00:36:07,540
I copied some Buddhist Scripture,

683
00:36:07,620 --> 00:36:09,540
which will keep our Xu Family safe.

684
00:36:10,540 --> 00:36:12,820
That's very thoughtful of you!

685
00:36:14,620 --> 00:36:15,540
Great Madam,

686
00:36:15,700 --> 00:36:16,820
why don't we let them

687
00:36:16,940 --> 00:36:18,180
join us for breakfast?

688
00:36:18,820 --> 00:36:19,540
They will go back

689
00:36:19,620 --> 00:36:21,340
to their own places to eat.

690
00:36:21,460 --> 00:36:23,180
Just take care of yourself.

691
00:36:23,340 --> 00:36:24,340
Eat more.

692
00:36:25,340 --> 00:36:26,580
Look at you.

693
00:36:26,700 --> 00:36:27,780
Here, eat some more!

694
00:36:29,020 --> 00:36:30,700
Great Madam is treating you

695
00:36:30,780 --> 00:36:32,940
as her own daughter!

696
00:36:33,100 --> 00:36:35,060
You are right about that!

697
00:36:35,220 --> 00:36:36,660
I've been treating

698
00:36:36,780 --> 00:36:37,260
Lianfang as my daughter

699
00:36:37,380 --> 00:36:39,300
since she was little.

700
00:36:39,660 --> 00:36:40,940
And now I'm so happy

701
00:36:41,100 --> 00:36:42,900
that she's become family.

702
00:36:44,140 --> 00:36:45,420
Great Madam,

703
00:36:45,540 --> 00:36:46,800
I haven't offered tea
to Her Ladyship yet.

704
00:36:48,620 --> 00:36:50,100
Please enjoy your breakfast,

705
00:36:51,100 --> 00:36:52,340
I'll take my leave now.

706
00:36:52,540 --> 00:36:54,540
What a thoughtful kid!

707
00:36:54,660 --> 00:36:55,460
Go ahead.

708
00:37:02,940 --> 00:37:03,860
You two!

709
00:37:03,980 --> 00:37:05,460
Why are you still standing there?

710
00:37:05,740 --> 00:37:08,260
Go back and have your breakfast!

711
00:37:10,580 --> 00:37:11,260
Yes.

712
00:37:11,380 --> 00:37:12,220
Go.

713
00:37:16,100 --> 00:37:17,340
She asked the two Concubines

714
00:37:17,460 --> 00:37:18,620
to serve her breakfast

715
00:37:18,940 --> 00:37:20,380
and said in public

716
00:37:20,500 --> 00:37:21,900
that she'll have her back.

717
00:37:22,420 --> 00:37:23,820
I think Great Madam

718
00:37:23,940 --> 00:37:25,660
favors her too much!

719
00:37:25,940 --> 00:37:27,580
She's just a concubine now.

720
00:37:27,700 --> 00:37:30,460
If she replaced you as she wishes,

721
00:37:30,500 --> 00:37:32,700
then... then our Zhun

722
00:37:32,700 --> 00:37:34,140
would have a hard life from now on.

723
00:37:35,300 --> 00:37:36,460
Mother just pities her

724
00:37:36,580 --> 00:37:37,540
on the account

725
00:37:37,620 --> 00:37:38,820
of Concubine Qiao.

726
00:37:40,740 --> 00:37:42,140
As a concubine,

727
00:37:42,620 --> 00:37:44,260
she won't be a problem to us.

728
00:37:49,420 --> 00:37:51,740
Your Ladyship, Concubine Qiao is here.

729
00:37:55,500 --> 00:37:56,660
Let her in.

730
00:37:56,980 --> 00:37:57,620
Yes.

731
00:38:11,900 --> 00:38:14,060
I'm here to greet you, sister!

732
00:38:14,980 --> 00:38:17,500
Are you getting better, sister?

733
00:38:18,860 --> 00:38:20,940
I could die at any time.

734
00:38:21,260 --> 00:38:23,300
How can I get any better?

735
00:38:25,020 --> 00:38:26,740
Sister, don't think too much.

736
00:38:27,060 --> 00:38:29,380
Just take it easy and rest well.

737
00:38:35,460 --> 00:38:36,380
Madam,

738
00:38:36,580 --> 00:38:37,460
offer tea.

739
00:38:43,540 --> 00:38:44,340
Sister.

740
00:38:51,580 --> 00:38:52,300
Kneel.

741
00:39:11,980 --> 00:39:13,820
Sister, please have some tea!

742
00:39:50,020 --> 00:39:52,740
♪In the cold darkness of midnight,
a sigh is heard♪

743
00:39:53,380 --> 00:39:56,140
♪Who picked up the paintbrush
to draw loneliness♪

744
00:39:57,460 --> 00:40:04,020
♪In my life, I can draw everything,
but lovesickness♪

745
00:40:04,460 --> 00:40:06,500
♪The mountain city is waiting for rain♪

746
00:40:07,500 --> 00:40:11,100
♪I am waiting for you
to pass in my memory♪

747
00:40:11,540 --> 00:40:17,700
♪The sky is in a more lonely color
than your face♪

748
00:40:18,140 --> 00:40:20,660
♪The wind rises
and the candle light flickers♪

749
00:40:21,580 --> 00:40:24,140
♪The thin clothes
can't stand the cold days♪

750
00:40:25,340 --> 00:40:32,180
♪Full of twists and turns,
fate is untold♪

751
00:40:32,580 --> 00:40:34,780
♪I ground my thoughts into ink♪

752
00:40:35,780 --> 00:40:39,220
♪But I still can't sketch your contours♪

753
00:40:39,740 --> 00:40:45,500
♪How could the ink
and paper exhaust our stories♪

754
00:40:46,340 --> 00:40:53,220
♪Who picked up the pen
to disturb the heart♪

755
00:40:53,580 --> 00:41:00,220
♪Who visited to remind me of the past♪

756
00:41:00,620 --> 00:41:03,940
♪If feelings can be kept in mind,
but cannot be confessed♪

757
00:41:05,300 --> 00:41:07,340
♪I won't escape from whatever end♪

758
00:41:08,820 --> 00:41:14,540
♪In the dim lantern light,
with you there is me♪

759
00:41:14,540 --> 00:41:21,460
♪Who picked up the pen
to set free lonely tears♪

760
00:41:21,700 --> 00:41:28,220
♪Whoever visited my life,
only you stayed all the days♪

761
00:41:28,780 --> 00:41:32,300
♪If the moth doesn't fly into the fire♪

762
00:41:33,380 --> 00:41:36,340
♪How can it be said to be persistent♪

763
00:41:36,820 --> 00:41:44,460
♪Coming to the end of your story,
there is me♪
